# PHYSICS::DETACH_ROPE_FROM_ENTITY

## Summary
Detach rope from an entity. Rope should have been attached to this entity( not mandatory )

## Parameters
* **ROPE_INDEX** ropeID
* **ENTITY_INDEX** entityID
